And once he is in the city, <RP Category='POPE_TAG'>the <HR>Pope</HR></RP>, who is considered by many Serbs to have supported their adversaries, would be in range of sniper fire.

Mr. Navarro-Valls, <RP Category='POPE_TAG'>the <HR>Pope</HR></RP>'s spokesman, sought to rule out the idea that, if the Sarajevo trip was canceled, it would be because of <RP Category='POPE_TAG'>the <HR>Pope</HR></RP>'s poor health.

That leg, which by the way is clinically healed, will not be the thing which prevents <RP Category='POPE_TAG'>the <HR>Pope</HR></RP> from going to Sarajevo, he said today.
